trans-unit.source: The TrustRelationshipInformation class contains information for a trust relationship between a pair of <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"></xref> objects.

Obtains the name of the source <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"></xref> objects for this trust relationship.

A string that contains the name of the source <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"></xref> objects for this trust relationship.

Obtains the name of the target <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"></xref> objects for this trust relationship.

A string that contains the name of the target <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"></xref> objects for this trust relationship.

Obtains the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustDirection"></xref> objects for this trust relationship relative to the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"></xref> objects that created the trust.

A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustDirection"></xref> value for this trust relationship relative to the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"></xref> objects that created the trust.
Obtains the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustType"></xref> object of the trust relationship.
A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustType"></xref> value that represents the type of the trust relationship.
